            <p class="comment-content">“我们首先撑开阳伞，在地面上投射出阴影，在阴影中我们落成了一栋房子。”——谷崎润一郎</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="665049375">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-665049375" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-665049375" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="665049375">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/fishniao/">恶鸟</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2013-04-09</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">可惜是黑白的</p>
        </div>
